From cc5d01fb9e2de0ce4a30c39051e044efe86dff5d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sidhanta Sahu <sidhanta.sahu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 5 Nov 2024 04:26:26 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 21/24] UPSTREAM:CP:DP:wifi:ath12k: Add telemetry stats for QCA
 Energy Service
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Implement telemetry stats collection for QCA Energy Service:

Capture ath12k_pdev_telemetry_stats via WMI_CTRL_PATH_STATS_EVENTID
Capture ath12k_peer_telemetry_stats via HTT PPDU TX and PPDU DP MON path
Fetch these stats from the TLVs in each PPDU’s user info.
Add new members to existing data structures to store and update the
telemetry stats.

Patch-dependency: None

Signed-off-by: Sidhanta Sahu <sidhanta.sahu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Aloka Dixit <aloka.dixit@oss.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_htt.c | 6 +++++-
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_htt.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_htt.c
@@ -793,9 +793,13 @@ ath12k_dp_htt_ppdu_stats_update_tx_comp_
 	int i;
 
 	lockdep_assert_held(&ar->data_lock);
+
+	ath12k_htt_update_ppdu_stats(dp_pdev, ppdu_info);
+	/* Update below stats when msdu update path is disabled, It is likely
+	 * the case when KPI is enabled
+	 */
 	if (!ab->stats_disable)
 		return;
-	ath12k_htt_update_ppdu_stats(dp_pdev, ppdu_info);
 
 	for (i = 0; i < ppdu_info->ppdu_stats.common.num_users; i++) {
 		usr_stats = &ppdu_info->ppdu_stats.user_stats[i];
